        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Small Business Flexibility Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill provides&amp;nbsp;statutory authority for the pooling of tips among&amp;nbsp;two pools of employees. The first pool consists of employees who&amp;nbsp;customarily and regularly receive tips&amp;nbsp;(as is permitted under the current statute). The second pool consists of&amp;nbsp;(1) employees who&amp;nbsp;customarily and regularly receive tips and are paid at least minimum wage, and (2) employees who&amp;nbsp;do not customarily and regularly receive tips.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
